<title>MEXICO: Boehringer Ingelheim-Promeco to invest in Mexico.</title>
<headline>Boehringer Ingelheim-Promeco to invest in Mexico.</headline>
<dateline>MEXICO CITY 1996-09-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Pharmaceutical maker Boehringer Ingelheim-Promeco said that it will invest $70 million in a new production plant in Mexico.</p>
<p>The company said the new plant will allow it to sell more pharmaceuticals in North America.</p>
<p>It said that it hopes to export about $100 million in health products to the United States and Canada by the year 2000.</p>
<p>-- Mexico City newroom (525) 728 9559</p>
